parameters.name: partner_id
parameters.description: Partner id. Required for all requests

parameters.name: timestamp
parameters.description: Request timestamp in seconds from epoch. Required for all requests. Expires in 5 minutes

parameters.name: expire_token
parameters.description: This token for only works under 6 hours from generation, for api. Valid for multiple use and expires in 6 hours

parameters.name: error
parameters.description: Indicate error type if hit error. Empty if no error

parameters.name: message
parameters.description: Indicate error detail if hit error. Empty if no error

parameters.name: request_id
parameters.description: The identifier for an API request (for error tracking)
